<div class="markdown"><p>To see the difference in running time, we can compare the output <code>@benchmark</code> for both:</p></div>

<pre class='language-julia'><code class='language-julia'>using BenchmarkTools: @benchmark</code></pre>


<pre class='language-julia'><code class='language-julia'>@benchmark outer(2)</code></pre>
